{"word":"ἀνασκευάζω","slug":"ἀνασκευάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀνασϰευάζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, σϰευάζω</el> ‘prepare, make ready’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σκεῦος\">σκεῦος</a></el>; ‘to cause an entity to be packed up’, hence ‘dismantle, destroy’] <b><i>demolish, tear down,</i></b> in imagery = <i>upset, subvert</i> <b><a href='B:510 15:24'>Ac 15:24</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ opp.\">opp.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οἰκοδομέω\">οἰκοδομέω</a></el> <a href='B:510 9:31'>Ac 9:31</a>). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνασείω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνασπάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}